  "market_context": "On 26 April 2024, NQ1! had formed a swing low and reversed after reaching into a fair value gap on the daily chart. Price closed above the previous day high, setting a bullish bias and targeting the next buy-side liquidity level near 17810.",
  "key_observation": "London session consolidated without reaching any higher time frame PD array. At the 08:30 New York open, price made a manipulation move lower, sweeping sell-side liquidity, before closing above a series of down-close candles on the 5-minute chart, signaling a change in the state of delivery to the upside.",
  "analysis_steps": [
    "Step 1: Reviewed the daily chart and observed three days of expansion forming a swing low, a reversal into a fair value gap, and a close above the previous day high — establishing a bullish bias targeting the next previous day high.",
    "Step 2: Dropped to the 15-minute chart and observed that London session mostly consolidated, failing to reach any higher time frame PD array, consistent with a NY Manipulation daily profile setup.",
    "Step 3: Anticipated that the manipulation move would occur at either 08:30 or 09:30 New York time; observed that at 08:30 price initially moved up (manipulation higher), then reversed lower.",
    "Step 4: Dropped to the 5-minute chart to monitor for a change in the state of delivery; noted that price took out a prior swing low, then attempted to close above the high needed to confirm CHoCH — which initially failed as price made a new low.",
    "Step 5: Observed that price could not displace below the new low, and at the New York open (09:30) price closed above a down-close candle, confirming the change in the state of delivery (CHoCH).",
    "Step 6: Used the 5-minute CHoCH candle close to frame a long entry, placed stop-loss below the manipulation low, and set the target at the previous day high (~17810).",
    "Step 7: Confirmed the trade was filled and price subsequently reached and took out the previous day high target."
  ],
  "outcome": "Long entry triggered on 5-minute CHoCH confirmation; stop placed below the manipulation low; target at previous day high (~17810) was successfully reached and filled.",
